reviewText: This DVD is perfect for mature and more arthritic people.  Tony is a little "cheesey" at times but overall a very good instructor.  Hope this helps others who are thinking of making a purchase.
I had this DVD when I purchased the Gazella and misplaceds.  It was in the orginal package, great find.  I can enjoy my Gazella again.
This replaced old VHS when I purchased the Gazelle.  Love it.  Now I can start really using the Gazelle better.
He liked the fact that it was light in weight, but he had nothing to compare it to. I, on the other-hand have one that is heavy duty and felt this was a knock off brand.
what a workout and it works! perfect for arthritis i think this is the best thing hes made! love it.

Even though this DVD is very old, it is still a great workout.  I have had my gazelle for years now, but only recently learned some of the different moves.  The gazelle is a great workout for 'mature exercisers'.  Luv it!

We are hoping this will not be another clothes rack!  So, far, it seems to be a good work-out.  It appears that it is not too hard on the knees which is the reason it was  purchased.  It was not difficult to put together, and was shipped promptly.
I did not find this video as motivating as I thought it might be based on the review I had read about it. I certainly didn't think it was worth the money and it certainly is not a TOTAL BODY WORKOUT.
